MORRISTOWN HORSE SHOW HELD IN RAIN; 
Children's Pony Jumping Class One of the New Features of Exhibition
<i>New York Times</i>, 8 October 1915:
&quot;Five children, none over 15 years, took part in the pony jumping class...Miss Ruth Brady rode Miss Helen Fiske's Maidstone, with which she took the reserve....&quot;
Could this portrait be the same equestrian Miss Ruth Brady, a few years later?
